'''Symt''' was the [[Capital/Legends|capital]] [[City/Legends|city]] of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Darstell 4]]. The [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Governor/Legends|Governor's]] palace was located in thecenter of the city. Symt had a fairly high level of technology, with approximately one million [[Sentience/Legends|beings]] calling it home. It contained a modest underworld element, as well as a fair amount of crime, although its small size kept things from getting tremendously out of hand. It had a large Imperial presence, with many [[Stormtrooper/Legends|Stormtroopers]] patrolling the city whenever Governor [[Bellows]] requested it.
